{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0b5b47a529","title":"两张大字报：“反对外行领导内行”、“人民呼声”","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选辑(第二集)》(南开大学社会主义思想教育教研组，1957.10)。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47d0adb343","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"0b5b47a529"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"18bdcc9c77","name":"阎树栋"},{"id":"2dda8f3877","name":"陈本敬"},{"id":"f10ac419e8","name":"章迺汉"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"eeba96b606","type":"title","text":"两张大字报：“反对外行领导内行”、“人民呼声”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"5cd9d1c96d","type":"authors","text":"南开大学陈本敬阎树栋章迺汉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"17711d1e04","type":"subtitle","text":"[陈本敬：南开大学物理系助教；阎树栋、章迺汉：南开大学数学系助教]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"9d6e4d7318","type":"paragraph","text":"第一张大字报：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"19c6bbb71e","type":"paragraph","text":"1、反对外行领导内行。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"957fd2b950","type":"paragraph","text":"2、要求人事材料公开。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"39d6a629aa","type":"paragraph","text":"3、要求有科学研究及图书、仪器。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"cd1c241040","type":"paragraph","text":"4、要求重视青年教师。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"da35953740","type":"paragraph","text":"5、要国务院像重视工业一样的重视科学。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"c88a63ea4f","type":"paragraph","text":"6、反对将工农速中的学生保送入大学。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"81ed2945ed","type":"paragraph","text":"7、反对党团员有特殊权利的大裙带关系。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"561a2ce33f","type":"paragraph","text":"第二张大字报：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"bd0b61c06a","type":"paragraph","text":"人民呼声","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"d2e2e0c438","type":"paragraph","text":"争自由、争民主、争人权","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"4bc869e69f","type":"paragraph","text":"打碎黑罐撕破黑带，反对愚民政策，实行信仰自由，支持同学的意见，选修政治课。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"4c1157f027","type":"paragraph","text":"要求通过真正的民主，选举人民代表；反对包办式的选举制。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"fc30668c50","type":"paragraph","text":"对祖国科学事业负责，对青年负责；反对留助教，派留学生，升等升级，开课重德不重才的卑鄙制度。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"},{"id":"9a310d9200","type":"paragraph","text":"给青年助教以合理工资待遇。反对把头制；不学无术的人退出学校的领导地位。人类灵魂的工程师们不要沉默了，让我们参加到同学们的斗争行列中去！","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529"}],"page":{"id":"465adec4b9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0b5b47a529","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}